body: I think this comment needs to be elaborated, because we had a pretty long discussion about what is going on here, and it needs to be clear that this code is responsible for eliminating the correspondence between `state_dict` and the parameters of an exported ONNX model, so basically you are SOL if you want to manually interpret the parameters.
